short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A Chrome Extension to improve browsing history experience

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Chrome-Wrapped is an advanced browsing history companion extension, which provides graphs and and search features to better visualize a user's browsing history. 

Source code available on GitHub: github.com/comp195/senior-project-spring-2023-chrome-wrapped

Report any bugs/feature requests on our form:
https://forms.gle/7hnGy6iebANHyCTCA
